	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, I came across a level 13 ogre warrior named Largemarge on Tarew Marr about 2 days ago in S.RO. She asked me about weapons and dual weilding, and the fact that she was looking for some new gear. Well I told her that I had a Centi Warspear (paid only 20pp in the Bazaar for it) and a Jarsath Trident (paid 200pp in Bazaar). She said she would be interested in those, but all the had to trade for it was the Heavy Velium War Lance. I did not know what it was worth, so i offered to trade her both and 150pp for it. Suffice to say, with a 169 STR and a pierce skill of 154, I avg hit between 67 and 99. Doing non-crit hits for up to 110, and crits for 170. Near ahd a cow when I hit a Crippling Blow for 387. <br>&nbsp;<br>Give an NPC a torch, and you will warm him for 30 minutes. Set an NPC on fire, and you will warm him for the rest of his life.</td></tr>
